34
00:02:15,820 --> 00:02:17,260
Because I respect you.

35
00:02:19,260 --> 00:02:20,180
If you are willing

36
00:02:21,260 --> 00:02:23,380
to share your secret one day,

37
00:02:24,020 --> 00:02:25,540
I will bear whatever difficulty

38
00:02:25,540 --> 00:02:26,580
for you.

39
00:02:27,300 --> 00:02:28,700
But if you don't want to tell,

40
00:02:29,100 --> 00:02:30,860
I will also protect you
with all my heart.

41
00:02:38,820 --> 00:02:40,220
I have already designed

42
00:02:40,300 --> 00:02:41,180
