56
00:03:19,460 --> 00:03:24,220
♪Swinging through autumn
to Stone Bridge Bay♪

57
00:03:24,220 --> 00:03:26,100
My disciple is intelligent.

58
00:03:26,340 --> 00:03:27,340
If one has to be blamed,

59
00:03:27,940 --> 00:03:29,220
it must be me.

60
00:03:29,220 --> 00:03:31,910
♪In the land of dreams,
love sparks into wildfire♪

61
00:03:31,910 --> 00:03:34,860
♪Radiant as the night sky,
setting the city aflame♪

62
00:03:34,860 --> 00:03:35,780
Thank you,

63
00:03:36,740 --> 00:03:37,380
Xiaosheng.

64
00:03:37,380 --> 00:03:40,240
♪Though trapped in deep mud♪

65
00:03:40,240 --> 00:03:43,360
♪I fear no changes♪

66
00:03:43,360 --> 00:03:48,000
♪I intend on walking with you
till the end♪

67
00:03:48,000 --> 00:03:52,630
♪In the land of dreams,
I stay with you forever♪

68
00:03:52,900 --> 00:03:53,700
Say that again.

69
00:03:53,700 --> 00:03:57,700
♪Let gossip and doubts dissolve
into the mist♪

70
00:03:57,700 --> 00:03:58,500
Xiaosheng.

71
00:03:58,500 --> 00:04:01,840
♪Should enigmas unravel♪

72
00:04:01,840 --> 00:04:05,030
♪It's surely the divine grace♪

73
00:04:05,030 --> 00:04:10,080
♪Together, we conclude our tale♪

74
00:04:21,430 --> 00:04:25,120
♪As twilight lingers♪

75
00:04:26,390 --> 00:04:28,300
♪Swallows whisper, their dance begins♪

76
00:04:28,300 --> 00:04:29,420
Brother, it's getting late.

77
00:04:29,740 --> 00:04:30,620
I'm going to bed.

78
00:04:32,240 --> 00:04:37,600
♪By the water, a beauty stands,
lights dimly lit♪

79
00:04:37,600 --> 00:04:42,630
♪Her hands gently play the zither,
sharing this moment with you♪

80
00:04:50,860 --> 00:04:51,340
Brother.

81
00:04:51,860 --> 00:04:52,820
I'm curious about one thing.

82
00:04:53,340 --> 00:04:54,820
Before I joined
the Blood Sacrifice Gang,

83
00:04:54,820 --> 00:04:56,460
who used to be your female partner?

84
00:04:57,940 --> 00:04:58,620
Really?

85
00:04:58,620 --> 00:04:59,500
I didn't know that.

86
00:05:01,260 --> 00:05:02,020
The chief said

87
00:05:02,020 --> 00:05:03,300
you are very experienced
in duo tasks.

88
00:05:04,700 --> 00:05:05,740
Chief is getting old.

89
00:05:06,100 --> 00:05:06,700
He must've remembered it wrong.

90
00:05:07,620 --> 00:05:08,220
Has he?

91
00:05:08,620 --> 00:05:10,300
If so, I should ask him after this.

92
00:05:12,100 --> 00:05:13,740
Well, you know what?

93
00:05:15,620 --> 00:05:17,060
Gold bars and jewelry?

94
00:05:19,140 --> 00:05:20,180
You can't waste money like that.

95
00:05:22,260 --> 00:05:22,700
Come.

96
00:05:25,380 --> 00:05:26,860
Make it look more convincing.

97
00:05:28,380 --> 00:05:29,620
We have to let others trust

98
00:05:29,620 --> 00:05:31,700
