99
00:05:31,700 --> 00:05:32,380
I'm sorry.

100
00:05:37,420 --> 00:05:38,900
If you can make me happy,

101
00:05:39,340 --> 00:05:40,980
I will buy you

102
00:05:41,100 --> 00:05:41,900
silver jewelry next time.

103
00:05:42,260 --> 00:05:43,780
I'm very close with
the owner of the jewelry store.

104
00:05:45,020 --> 00:05:46,100
Jerk, come out!

105
00:05:50,300 --> 00:05:50,620
How dare you

106
00:05:51,020 --> 00:05:52,300
come to the dance hall!

107
00:05:52,300 --> 00:05:53,500
You are dead meat!

108
00:05:55,220 --> 00:05:55,940
Dear.

109
00:05:57,340 --> 00:05:58,340
Dear, I'm sorry.

110
00:05:58,340 --> 00:05:58,980
Dear.

111
00:05:59,980 --> 00:06:00,380
Stop right there!

112
00:06:00,900 --> 00:06:01,220
Dear.

113
00:06:01,780 --> 00:06:02,100
Dear.

114
00:06:02,700 --> 00:06:03,220
Dear, it's my fault.

115
00:06:03,220 --> 00:06:03,540
Dear.

116
00:06:04,380 --> 00:06:04,700
Stop!

117
00:06:05,180 --> 00:06:06,020
She is beating me.

118
00:06:07,940 --> 00:06:08,180
Dear.

119
00:06:08,180 --> 00:06:08,500
Stop right there!

120
00:06:11,860 --> 00:06:12,100
Dear.

121
00:06:13,140 --> 00:06:13,900
Dear, forgive me.

122
00:06:14,340 --> 00:06:15,100
Stop running!

123
00:06:17,060 --> 00:06:17,300
Dear.

124
00:06:19,060 --> 00:06:19,660
Dear.

125
00:06:22,260 --> 00:06:22,980
You are still running?

126
00:06:25,500 --> 00:06:26,140
Come here.

127
00:06:27,420 --> 00:06:27,980
Are you insane?

128
00:06:27,980 --> 00:06:29,460
I'm so sorry.

129
00:06:31,260 --> 00:06:31,620
Dear.

130
00:06:32,980 --> 00:06:33,780
Dear.

131
00:06:37,580 --> 00:06:38,260
Dear.

132
00:06:38,260 --> 00:06:39,260
I'm going to beat you to death!

133
00:06:40,700 --> 00:06:41,660
I'm sorry, Dear.

134
00:06:41,660 --> 00:06:41,900
Miss Xu, right?

135
00:06:41,900 --> 00:06:43,060
I won't come here again!

136
00:06:44,420 --> 00:06:45,380
I mean it. I dare not come here again!

137
00:06:46,300 --> 00:06:47,180
Go that way.

138
00:06:48,420 --> 00:06:48,940
Dear.

139
00:06:54,860 --> 00:06:55,860
You are not going anywhere.

140
00:07:03,620 --> 00:07:04,540
As you instructed,

141
00:07:04,940 --> 00:07:06,180
