142
00:07:07,100 --> 00:07:09,020
Those who are involved
are injured or crippled,

143
00:07:09,380 --> 00:07:10,100
but not fatally.

144
00:07:13,700 --> 00:07:14,220
All right.

145
00:07:15,100 --> 00:07:16,900
This is your reward.

146
00:07:17,780 --> 00:07:18,500
- Thank you, sir.
- Thank you, sir.

147
00:07:22,540 --> 00:07:23,100
Qingming.

148
00:07:23,820 --> 00:07:24,660
It wasn't dangerous.

149
00:07:24,900 --> 00:07:25,820
