150
00:07:31,060 --> 00:07:31,620
It's fine.

151
00:07:32,100 --> 00:07:33,620
I was whipped by accident.

152
00:07:34,620 --> 00:07:35,540
Be more careful next time.

153
00:07:35,700 --> 00:07:36,140
Yes.

154
00:08:01,380 --> 00:08:02,300
