160
00:09:46,700 --> 00:09:47,260
It hurts.

161
00:09:49,240 --> 00:09:55,000
♪A glance seals our fate♪

162
00:09:55,180 --> 00:09:55,740
It does hurt.

163
00:09:55,840 --> 00:10:01,550
♪Without you, time fades into night♪

164
00:10:02,320 --> 00:10:08,750
♪My heart adrift,
seeking wings to break free♪

165
00:10:09,440 --> 00:10:14,480
♪Through tears, our love endures♪

166
00:10:15,150 --> 00:10:17,750
♪Fate entwined♪

167
00:10:18,200 --> 00:10:20,870
♪Love and hatred intertwined♪

168
00:10:21,600 --> 00:10:27,720
♪My sorrow overwhelmed.
I gaze at the moon, longing for you♪

169
